<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Glue" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Glue,</orth> vb. to join with a viscous substance: <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.4.65" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 4, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 2, 38</bibl>. In a figurative sense: <bibl n="shak. ven 546" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 546</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 5</bibl>.
